      "inputs": [],
      "outputs": [],
      "properties": {},
      "widgets_values": [
        "# Fish Audio S2 TTS\n\n## Auto-Download\n\n**Models auto-download on first run** - no manual setup needed!\n\n| Model | VRAM | Size |\n|-------|------|------|\n| s2-pro (bf16) | ~24GB | ~10GB |\n| s2-pro-fp8 | ~20GB | ~8GB |\n| s2-pro-BNB-int8 | ~20GB | ~10GB |\n| s2-pro-BNB-nf4 | ~16GB  | ~10GB  |\n---\n\n## Manual Download\n\n| File | Size | Link |\n|------|------|------|\n| s2-pro (Full) | ~10GB | [Download](https://huggingface.co/fishaudio/s2-pro) |\n| s2-pro-fp8 | ~8GB | [Download](https://huggingface.co/drbaph/s2-pro-fp8) |\n\n\nPlace in:\n```\nComfyUI/models/FishAudioS2/\n├── s2-pro/\n│   ├── config.json\n│   ├── model.safetensors\n│   └── ...\n└── s2-pro-fp8/\n    ├── config.json\n    ├── model.safetensors\n    └── ...\n```\n\n---\n\n## BNB Model use the s2-pro model as base and quantise on the fly using bitsandbytes\n\n---\n\n## Common tags (15,000+ unique tags supported):\n\n## [pause] [emphasis] [laughing] [inhale] [chuckle] [tsk] [singing] [excited] [laughing tone] [interrupting] [chuckling] [excited tone] [volume up] [echo] [angry] [low volume] [sigh] [low voice] [whisper] [screaming] [shouting] [loud] [surprised] [short pause] [exhale] [delight] [panting] [audience laughter] [with strong accent] [volume down] [clearing throat] [sad] [moaning] [shocked]\n\n---\n\n## Links\n\n- Original [fish-speech](https://github.com/fishaudio/fish-speech)\n- Models [s2-pro](https://huggingface.co/fishaudio/s2-pro) / [s2-pro-fp8](https://huggingface.co/drbaph/s2-pro-fp8)\n- Issues [Report Bug](https://github.com/Saganaki22/ComfyUI-FishAudioS2/issues)"
      ],
      "color": "#c09430",
      "bgcolor": "rgba(24,24,27,.9)"
    },
